Rating: 3
This was EASY and good, but I did alter it a tad. Cut the olive oil out (why would you use it with fatty bacon anyway?) and then reduced whipping cream to 1/3 cup and ADDED 1/3 cup of chicken broth. At first seems saucy, but in min. after adding the cheese at end, the pasta absorbs all the liquid. Thus this wasn't dry at all. Good one to make quickly after coming home from work.

